     p.lead SportsZone gives you all the latest news and gist in football.
     p.lead Since Ballon D’Or has parted company with FIFA, the world football governing body has brought their own “The Best FIFA Football award” starting for the caledar year 2016. The ceremony will be taking place on Monday Night, 09 January 2017 at the FIFA headquarters in Zurich, Switzerland. There will be number of awards given out on the night which include mens and women best footballer of the year, coach of the year and FIFA Puskas (best goal of the year) awards. We take a look at how you can watch the ceremony live.


