      p.lead Jose Mourinho was delighted with Manchester United's change in attitude after they bounced back from defeat at Huddersfield to beat Swansea 2-0.

      p.lead United progressed to the Carabao Cup quarter-final thanks to goals in either half by Jesse Lingard, coming days after their below-par showing at Huddersfield in the Premier League.

